Correct
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Cutting at 1 and then making a false eye with 3 and 5 is the only way to capture the cutting stones. This eay Black can connect all his own stones and is very happy.
\par }
