Wrong
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par When Black pushes at 1, White is happy to connect at 2. This way Black has to give up on his center stones and the precious  white cutting stones. What a pity.
\par }
